When you say:

“Move the muscles and crawl the action potential across your body,”

that is exactly what’s happening — just through voluntary recruitment, not literal conscious control of action potentials.

You’re using:

Motor Imagery → Motor Unit Recruitment Pathways

The same pathways used to learn:
	•	trigger squeeze isolation
